com.ibm.jaggr.service

Class InitParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.jaggr.service.InitParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<InitParams.InitParam>

    public class InitParams
extends Object
implements Iterable<InitParams.InitParam>
    Wrapper class for aggregator init-params.

    Init params are specified with the init-param attribute in the servlet element of the org.eclipse.equinox.http.registry.servlets extension point.

      • OPTIONS_INITPARAM

        public static final String OPTIONS_INITPARAM
        Name of the servlet init-param that specifies the filename of the java properties file containing the aggregator options (see IOptions). If not specified, then the aggregator will look for options properties in the file aggregator.properties in the home directory of the user that started the aggregator.

        Constant Field Values
